title: Walt Disney Lustiges Taschenbuch English Edition
description:
Walt Disney Lustiges Taschenbuch English Edition Stories from Duckburg 

Vol 1-6, Disney Enterprises, Inc., 2009-2011, 276 pages each (1656 pages total)

Written by John Blair Moore, Pat & Carol McGreal, Lars Jensen, Paul Halas, Micheal T. Gilbert, Andreas Phil, Gorm Transgaard, Mark Shaw, Byron Erickson, Terry LaBan, Alessandro Perina, Laura Shaw, Carlo Panaro, Enzo Mina, Bruno Sardo, Sarah Kinney, Carl Barks, Geoffrey Blum, Peter Hopfner, Dave Rawson, Marco Rota, Jens Hansegard, Per-Erik Hedman 

Illustrated by Bancells, Miguel, Flemming Anderson, Gonzales, Massimo Fecchi, Maximino, Alessandro Perina, Luciano Marcato, Pasquale, Massimo De Vita, Anna Marabelli, Stefano De Lellis, Marco Rota, Giorgio Cavazzano, Joaquin, Ferioli


Each volume also contains a Character Files and Dictionary sections.
